Name: createdDate
Description: Date and time the contact was created. In ISO format.

Name: info.addresses.items
Description: Street address ID. (Note: seems to be optional, not present in test data)

Name: info.addresses.items
Description: Address type. Supported values: UNTAGGED, HOME, WORK, BILLING, SHIPPING. UNTAGGED is shown as Other" in the Contact List."

Name: info.birthdate
Description: Birth date in YYYY-MM-DD format. For example, 2020-03-15.

Name: info.emails.items
Description: Indicates whether this is the contact's primary email address. When changing primary to true for an email, the contact's other emails become false.

Name: info.emails.items
Description: Email type. Supported values: UNTAGGED, MAIN, HOME, WORK. UNTAGGED is shown as Other" in the Contact List"

Name: info.extendedFields
Description: This property isn't documented as it's a general structure

Name: info.jobTitle
Description: Contact's job title. Corresponds to the Position field in the Dashboard.

Name: info.labelKeys
Description: This property isn't documented as it's a general structure

Name: info.locale
Description: Locale in IETF BCP 47 language tag format. Typically, this is a lowercase 2-letter language code, followed by a hyphen, followed by an uppercase 2-letter country code. For example, en-US for U.S. English, and de-DE for Germany German.

Name: info.phones.items
Description: ITU E.164-formatted phone number. Automatically generated using phone and countryCode, as long as both of those values are valid.

Name: info.phones.items
Description: Whether this is the contact's primary phone number. When changing primary to true for a phone, the contact's other phones become false.

Name: info.phones.items
Description: Phone type. Supported values: UNTAGGED, MAIN, HOME, MOBILE, WORK, FAX. UNTAGGED is shown as Other" in the Contact List."

Name: info.picture.image.id
Description: WixMedia image ID. This property is written by Wix when an image is uploaded to the Wix Media Manager.

Name: info.picture.image.url
Description: Image source: Either a Media Manager URL or external URL.

Name: info.picture.image.urlExpirationDate
Description: Image URL expiration date (when relevant). Optional

Name: info.picture.imageProvider
Description: This property isn't documented in the docs

Name: lastActivity.activityDate
Description: Date and time of the last action. In ISO format.

Name: lastActivity.activityType
Description: Contact's last action in the site. Supported values: GENERAL, CONTACT_CREATED, MEMBER_LOGIN, MEMBER_REGISTER, MEMBER_STATUS_CHANGED, FORM_SUBMITTED, INBOX_FORM_SUBMITTED, INBOX_PAYMENT_REQUEST_PAID, INBOX_MESSAGE_TO_CUSTOMER, INBOX_MESSAGE_FROM_CUSTOMER, NEWSLETTER_SUBSCRIPTION_FORM_SUBMITTED, NEWSLETTER_SUBSCRIPTION_UNSUBSCRIBE, ECOM_PURCHASE, ECOM_CART_ABANDON, ECOM_CHECKOUT_BUYER, BOOKINGS_APPOINTMENT, HOTELS_RESERVATION, HOTELS_PURCHASE, HOTELS_CONFIRMATION, HOTELS_CANCEL, VIDEO_PURCHASE, VIDEO_RENT, CASHIER_BUTTON_PURCHASE, ARENA_NEW_LEAD, EVENTS_RSVP, INVOICE_PAY, INVOICE_OVERDUE, PRICE_QUOTE_ACCEPT, PRICE_QUOTE_EXPIRE, RESTAURANTS_ORDER, RESTAURANTS_RESERVATION, SHOUTOUT_OPEN, SHOUTOUT_CLICK, CONTACT_MERGED.

Name: picture.id
Description: WixMedia image ID. This property is written by Wix when an image is uploaded to the Wix Media Manager.

Name: picture.url
Description: Image source: Either a Media Manager URL or external URL.

Name: picture.urlExpirationDate
Description: Image URL expiration date (when relevant). Optional

Name: primaryInfo.email
Description: Primary email address. This property reflects the email address in info.emails where primary is true.

Name: primaryInfo.phone
Description: Primary phone number. This property reflects the phone number in info.phones where primary is true.

Name: revision
Description: Revision number, which increments by 1 each time the contact is updated. To prevent conflicting changes, the existing revision must be used when updating a contact.

Name: source.appId
Description: App ID, if the contact was created by an app.

Name: source.sourceType
Description: Source type. Supported values: OTHER, ADMIN, WIX_APP, IMPORT, THIRD_PARTY, WIX_BOOKINGS, WIX_CHAT, WIX_EMAIL_MARKETING, WIX_EVENTS, WIX_FORMS, WIX_GROUPS, WIX_HOTELS, WIX_MARKET_PLACE, WIX_MUSIC, WIX_RESTAURANTS, WIX_SITE_MEMBERS, WIX_STORES, WIX_CODE.

Name: source.wixAppId
Description: DEPRECATED: App ID, if the contact was created by a Wix app. Deprecation Notice: This property has been replaced with appId and will be removed on March 31, 2022. If your app uses this property, we recommend updating your code as soon as possible.

Name: updatedDate
Description: Date and time the contact was last updated.

Name: lastUpdated
Description: Last updated timestamp. Datetime in ISO format

Name: numericId
Description: Inventory’s unique numeric ID (assigned in ascending order). Primarily for sorting and filtering when crawling all inventories.

Name: preorderInfo.enabled
Description: Whether the item is available for preorder.

Name: preorderInfo.limit
Description: Number of products that can be preordered after stock reaches zero.

Name: preorderInfo.message
Description: A message the buyer will see when the item is out of stock and preorder is enabled.

Name: variants
Description: Whether the variant is available for preorder. When true, the variant is out of stock and preorder is enabled on inventory level.

Name: variants
Description: Whether the product is listed as in stock.

Name: variants
Description: Quantity currently left in inventory. Optional.

Name: activityStatus
Description: Member activity status. Supported values: UNKNOWN, ACTIVE, MUTED. ACTIVE: Member can write forum posts and blog comments. MUTED: Member cannot write forum posts or blog comments. UNKNOWN: Insufficient permissions to get the status.

Name: contact.addresses.items
Description: Street address ID. (Note: seems to be optional, not present in test data)

Name: contact.addresses.items
Description: Address type. Supported values: UNTAGGED, HOME, WORK, BILLING, SHIPPING. UNTAGGED is shown as Other" in the Contact List."

Name: contact.birthdate
Description: Birth date in YYYY-MM-DD format. For example, 2020-03-15.

Name: contact.emails.items

Name: contact.emails.items
Description: Email type. Supported values: UNTAGGED, MAIN, HOME, WORK. UNTAGGED is shown as Other" in the Contact List"

Name: contact.phones.items
Description: ITU E.164-formatted phone number. Automatically generated using phone and countryCode, as long as both of those values are valid.

Name: contact.phones.items
Description: Whether this is the contact's primary phone number. When changing primary to true for a phone, the contact's other phones become false.

Description: Phone type. Supported values: UNTAGGED, MAIN, HOME, MOBILE, WORK, FAX. UNTAGGED is shown as Other" in the Contact List."

Description: WixMedia image ID. This property is written by Wix when an image is uploaded to the Wix Media Manager.

Description: Image source: Either a Media Manager URL or external URL.

Name: contact.picture.image.urlExpirationDate

Name: createdDate
Description: Date and time when the member was created. ISO format.

Name: lastLoginDate
Description: Date and time when the member last logged in to the site. ISO format.

Name: loginEmail
Description: Email used by the member to log in to the site. Optional.

Name: privacyStatus
Description: Member privacy status. Supported values: UNKNOWN, PRIVATE, PUBLIC. PUBLIC: Member is visible to everyone. PRIVATE: Member is hidden from site visitors and other site members. Member is returned only to site contributors and apps with the appropriate permissions. UNKNOWN: Insufficient permissions to get the status.

Name: profile.cover.id
Description: WixMedia image ID. This property is written by Wix when an image is uploaded to the Wix Media Manager.

Name: profile.cover.url
Description: Image source: Either a Media Manager URL or external URL.

Name: profile.nickname
Description: Name that identifies the member to other members. Displayed on the member's profile page and interactions in the forum or blog.

Name: profile.photo.id
Description: WixMedia image ID. This property is written by Wix when an image is uploaded to the Wix Media Manager.

Name: profile.photo.url
Description: Image source: Either a Media Manager URL or external URL.

Name: profile.slug
Description: Slug that determines the member's profile page URL.

Name: profile.title
Description: Member title. Currently available through the API only.

Name: status
Description: Member site access status. Supported values: UNKNOWN, PENDING, APPROVED, BLOCKED, OFFLINE. PENDING: Member created and is waiting for approval by site owner. APPROVED: Member can log in to the site. OFFLINE: Member is a guest author for the site blog and cannot log in to the site. BLOCKED: Member is blocked and cannot log in to the site. UNKNOWN: Insufficient permissions to get the status.

Name: updatedDate
Description: Date and time when the member was updated. ISO format.

Name: activities
Description: Supported values: UNSPECIFIED_ORDER_HISTORY_ITEM_TYPE, MERCHANT_COMMENT, ORDER_PLACED, ORDER_PAID, ORDER_FULFILLED, ORDER_NOT_FULFILLED, DOWNLOAD_LINK_SENT, PICKUP_READY_EMAIL_SENT, TRACKING_NUMBER_ADDED, TRACKING_NUMBER_EDITED, TRACKING_LINK_WAS_SET, SHIPPING_CONFIRMATION_EMAIL_SENT, INVOICE_WAS_SET, INVOICE_WAS_REMOVED, INVOICE_WAS_SENT, FULFILLER_EMAIL_SENT, SHIPPING_ADDRESS_EDITED, EMAIL_EDITED, ORDER_PARTIALLY_PAID.

Name: archived
Description: Whether or not the order was archived.

Name: billingInfo.paymentMethod
Description: Payment method used for this order

Name: billingInfo.refundableByPaymentProvider
Description: Whether order can be refunded by payment provider (manually or automatic)

Name: buyerInfo.identityType
Description: Supported values: UNSPECIFIED_IDENTITY_TYPE, MEMBER, CONTACT. Customer type

Name: buyerInfo.type
Description: Deprecated (use identityType instead) Supported values: UNSPECIFIED_IDENTITY_TYPE, MEMBER, CONTACT.

Name: buyerLanguage
Description: Language for communication with the buyer. Defaults to the site language. For a site that supports multiple languages, this is the language the buyer selected.

Name: channelInfo.type
Description: Supported values: UNSPECIFIED, WEB, POS, EBAY, AMAZON, OTHER_PLATFORM, WIX_APP_STORE, WIX_INVOICES, BACKOFFICE_MERCHANT, WISH. Sales channel that submitted the order

Name: currency
Description: Currency used for the pricing of this order in ISO-4217 format.

Name: enteredBy.identityType
Description: Supported values: USER, MEMBER, CONTACT, APP.

Name: fulfillmentStatus
Description: Supported values: NOT_FULFILLED, FULFILLED, CANCELED, PARTIALLY_FULFILLED. Order's current fulfillment status (whether the order received a tracking number or was delivered/picked up).

Name: lastUpdated
Description: Date and time of latest update.

Name: lineItems
Description: Line item ID (auto-generated, stable within this order only)

Name: lineItems
Description: Supported values: NSPECIFIED_LINE_ITEM_TYPE, PHYSICAL, DIGITAL, CUSTOM_AMOUNT_ITEM. Line item type (may be extended)

Name: lineItems
Description: Line item product ID (optional for POS orders)

Name: lineItems
Description: Tax applied for this line item

Name: lineItems
Description: Product name, translated into the customer's language

Name: number
Description: Order number displayed in the owner's store (auto-generated).

Name: numericId
Description: Order’s unique numeric ID. Primarily used for sorting and filtering when crawling all orders.

Name: paymentStatus
Description: Supported values: UNSPECIFIED_PAYMENT_STATUS, NOT_PAID, PAID, PARTIALLY_REFUNDED, FULLY_REFUNDED, PENDING, PARTIALLY_PAID. Current status of the payment.

Name: shippingInfo.code
Description: Unique code of provided shipping option. For example, usps_std_overnight"."

Name: shippingInfo.shipmentDetails.priceData.taxIncludedInPrice
Description: Whether tax is included in the price.

Name: totals.subtotal
Description: Subtotal of all the line items, before tax.

Name: weightUnit
Description: Supported values: UNSPECIFIED_WEIGHT_UNIT, KG, LB. Weight unit used in this store.

Name: convertedPriceData.discountedPrice
Description: Discounted product price (if no discounted price is set, the product price is returned) (property can be decimal or integer).

Name: convertedPriceData.formatted.discountedPrice
Description: Discounted product price formatted with the currency (if no discounted price is set, the product formatted price is returned)

Name: convertedPriceData.formatted.price
Description: Product price formatted with the currency

Name: createdDate
Description: Date and time the product was created.

Name: discount.type
Description: Supported values: UNDEFINED, NONE, AMOUNT, PERCENT. Discount type: amount / percent

Name: id
Description: Product ID (generated automatically by the catalog).

Name: inventoryItemId
Description: Inventory item ID - ID referencing the inventory system.

Name: lastUpdated
Description: Date and time the product was last updated.

Name: manageVariants
Description: Whether variants are being managed for this product - enables unique SKU, price and weight per variant. Also affects inventory data.

Name: media.items
Description: Supported values: unspecified_media_item_type, image, video, audio, document, zip. Media item type (image, video, etc.).

Name: media.mainMedia.mediaType
Description: Supported values: unspecified_media_item_type, image, video, audio, document, zip. Media item type (image, video, etc.).

Name: numericId
Description: Product’s unique numeric ID (assigned in ascending order). Primarily used for sorting and filtering when crawling all products.

Name: price.currency
Description: Deprecated (use priceData instead). Product price currency

Name: price.discountedPrice
Description: Deprecated (use priceData instead). Discounted product price (if no discounted price is set, the product price is returned) (property can be decimal or integer).

Name: price.formatted.discountedPrice
Description: Deprecated (use priceData instead). Discounted product price (if no discounted price is set, the product price is returned)

Name: price.formatted.price
Description: Deprecated (use priceData instead). Product price formatted with the currency

Name: priceData.discountedPrice
Description: Discounted product price (if no discounted price is set, the product price is returned) (property can be decimal or integer).

Name: priceData.formatted.discountedPrice
Description: Discounted product price formatted with the currency (if no discounted price is set, the product formatted price is returned)

Name: priceData.formatted.price
Description: Product price formatted with the currency

Name: productOptions
Description: Supported values: unspecified_option_type, drop_down, color. Option type - color or other(drop down)

Name: productPageUrl.base
Description: Base URL. For premium sites, this is the domain. For free sites, this is the site URL (e.g mysite.wixsite.com/mysite).

Name: productPageUrl.path
Description: Path to the product page - e.g /product-page/a-product.

Name: ribbon
Description: Product ribbon. Used to highlight relevant information about a product. For example, Sale"

Name: slug
Description: A friendly URL name (generated automatically by the catalog when a product is created), can be updated.

Name: stock.inStock
Description: Whether the product is currently in stock (relevant only when tracking manually) Deprecated (use inventoryStatus instead)

Name: stock.inventoryStatus
Description: Supported values: IN_STOCK, OUT_OF_STOCK, PARTIALLY_OUT_OF_STOCK. The current status of the inventory: * IN_STOCK - In stock * OUT_OF_STOCK - Not in stock * PARTIALLY_OUT_OF_STOCK - Some of the variants are not in stock

Name: visible
Description: Whether the product is visible to site visitors.

Name: weight
Description: Product weight (if variant management is enabled, weight will be set per variant, and this field will be empty).
